y us It is not quite clear why Tuft Is hurrying home when Foraler Is keel t Ing so quiet The open season begins today Fa talities will bo reported in these col ums from time to time j If there is really anything In name the Cannon boom should make a great deal of noise when it gets to going ipnttyaanounces One packing company announces re duction in the prices of meat As Ar temus Ward used to remark This Is too much An exchange says he shortest life is the best In other words it doesnt do to give man time to show how mean he can be Is the American woman really beautiful asks a New York artist Well If she isnt there is no use mak ing further search The Hartford Herald complains that Democrats staid at home and did not vote at the recent election as If Re publicans were responsible for same The seasons kill In Vermont is re ported one hundred deer three guides and two"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2025-07-21T10:38:33.366Z", "group": ["ndnp/kyu", "university-of-kentucky-lexington-ky-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn86069313/1907-11-15/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:kyu:batch_kyu_gratefuldead_ver01:data:sn86069313:00175045557:1907111501:0378/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=463&w=318", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:kyu:batch_kyu_gratefuldead_ver01:data:sn86069313:00175045557:1907111501:0378/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=926&w=637", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/kyu/batch_kyu_gratefuldead_ver01/data/sn86069313/00175045557/1907111501/0378.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["kentucky", "united states", "ohio", "hartford", "ohio county"], "location_city": ["hartford"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["ohio"], "location_state": ["kentucky"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "applicatio